  "detailed_description": "Into the game, you will become a defender, return to the age of war, defense the enemy wave of attack.<br />\r\nYou can use submachine guns, heavy machine guns, grenades, mines, rockets, and other weapons to repel an enemy.<br />\r\nReach level S to unlock the next battle map。<br />\r\nTowns, wilderness, caves, battleships are all your battlefield.<br />\r\nAs more and more enemies become more and more difficult, defenders never back off!",
